snippet.title: What You Need About the Index Moving from LIBOR to SOFR
snippet.description:
There are important changes happening with ARMS you need to know about!
Join Finance of America Mortgage TPO, on Wednesday, August 12, 2020 at 11 am Pacific Time to find out what you need to know about the transition from London Interbank Offered Rate (LIBOR) to Secured Overnight Financing Rate (SOFR).

Changes are taking effect on your applications beginning in September 2020 that you want to be aware of!
